<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA621_04_IH_0007</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema621_04.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_04_ih_0007">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="7" class="is_star2">
					수 카드 4장 중 1장을 골라 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>안에 써넣어 몫이 가장 작은 (진분수)÷(진분수)의 나눗셈을 만들고 계산해 보세요.

				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box dir_col gap_60">
					<div class="img_box">
						<img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA621_04_IH/0007_img.svg" alt="">
					</div>
					<div class="flex gap_120">
						<div class="flex align_center">
							<div class="fraction_box">
								<span>9</span>
								<span>10</span>
							</div>
							÷
							<div class="fraction_box">
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
								</div>
								<span>8</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
							<math-field data-answer-single="1(1)/(35)(=(36)/(35))" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["1(1)/(35)", "(36)/(35)"]}'></math-field>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>몫이 가장 작으려면 나누는 수를 가장 크게 만들어야 하므로 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span> 안에 7을 써넣어야 합니다.</p>
								<p class="gap_0 mt_15">
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>9</span><span>10</span></span> ÷ <span class="fraction_box"><span>7</span><span>8</span></span> =
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>36</span><span>40</span></span> ÷
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>35</span><span>40</span></span> =
								  36 ÷ 35
								</p>
								<p class="gap_0 mt_15">
								  = <span class="fraction_box"><span>36</span><span>35</span></span>
								  = 1<span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>35</span></span>
								</p>
							  </div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve">
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
